{"tid":2003823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港今日沒有新增確診個案 已連續17天沒有本地感染個案","createTime":"2020-05-06T05:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T08:50:17.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"749c4ed09154affb7978f4791ab67c6850db4d1f","tid":2003823,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】5月6日新型冠狀病毒疫情消息一覽：<br />\n<br />\n最新：(1310)<br />\n<br />\n本港今日沒有新增確診個案，已連續17天沒有本地感染個案。<br />\n<br />\n政府：截至中午，銅芯抗疫口罩網上登記人數已超過100萬。<br />\n<br />\n康文署部分戶外康樂設施重開，轄下博物館及多間圖書館亦局部重開。<br />\n<br />\n限聚令周五放寬，婚禮聚集人數限制增至50人。<br />\n<br />\n戲院周五可重開，最多只可一半人入座，同一行最多連坐八人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390007&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=95234604\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390007&h=791975d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=390007</a>"},{"pid":"a4bda8ca58e8851ffdb58933794c47aad0815fd3","tid":2003823,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"😏"},{"pid":"93c81fcd9c8b40e21b6477e8b6ebc33526c16708","tid":2003823,"uid":99828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"然後政府終於派口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a52ce71c0dcf2024c2f4fe45953c1305db3064","tid":2003823,"uid":74163,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"袁國勇推算七成人染病料過萬人不治 食環署準備6個火葬場24小時運作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1950131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1950131</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n袁狗又中！"}]}